 />\n英文一定好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d1943c926c4e92353af0f0579677cbaee4031a","tid":229854,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Kentucky Fried Chicken<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 外國係人都咁叫，係香港人英文程度低先叫KFC....</blockquote><br />\nIn 1991, Kentucky Fried Chicken changed its name to&nbsp;KFC. Why, after 39 successful years, would a world-famous restaurant chain change its name?<br />\n<br />\nMaybe because KFC is just easier to say with your mouth full. Or maybe KFC fits better on signs. In reality, we wanted to let our customers know that we had more for them to enjoy than just fried chicken, and many were already calling us KFC, as it was much easier to say.<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦柒頭"},{"pid":"8cb8160f785b7f5d32ad6b356751fa61a5d031fc","tid":229854,"uid":14956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:00:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Kentucky Fried Chicken<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 外國係人都咁叫，係香港人英文程度低先叫KFC....</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6472b1ec263c44bc7fa31af831186b10934585","tid":229854,"uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:45:09.000Z","msg":"Kai Food Cafe"},{"pid":"df2d356087744cd1078d70ab877501392c49339a","tid":229854,"uid":7638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Kentucky Fried Chicken<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 外國係人都咁叫，係香港人英文程度低先叫KFC....</blockquote><br />\n咪係，全世界d鬼佬都唔會叫開dna架，叫開Deoxyribonucleic acid架<br />\n係我地呢d低等香港人先叫dna架咋...."},{"pid":"6d0ab26532f067c67768b3ec03d146c53166f84c","tid":229854,"uid":44476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Kentucky Frie